{"TopicId":142569,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Ask a physicist to speak at your funeral","CreatedByName":"RainDreamer","CreatedById":129077,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T00:44:03Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"RainDreamer","CreatedById":129077,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T00:44:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.iflscience.com/physics/ask-physicist-speak-your-funeral-0/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.iflscience.com/physics/ask-physicist-speak-your-funeral-0/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:\u0027Open Sans\u0027, sans-serif;font-size:14.28px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21.42px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003EYou want a physicist to speak at your funeral. You want the physicist to talk to your grieving family about the conservation of energy, so they will understand that your energy has not died. You want the physicist to remind your sobbing mother about the first law of thermodynamics; that no energy is created in the universe and none is destroyed. You want your mother to know that all your energy, ever vibration, every BTU of heat, every wave of every particle that was her beloved child remains with her in this world. You want the physicist to tell your weeping father that amid the energies of the cosmos, you gave as good as you got.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRead the whole article. Science is beautiful, and existence\u00A0after death is merely perspective.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T00:51:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow, that\u0027s brilliant.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frybert","CreatedById":97766,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T01:13:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T08:09:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOof! Right in the feelings \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;.;\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cry.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;.;\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Camacha","CreatedById":59088,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T13:02:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou mean you want a physisicst to remind everyone how futile your life was and that you were nothing more than a temporary collection of energy and information? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-27T21:00:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI once heard Neil DeGrasse Tyson say if he had to be sentenced to death, but could choose what happened to his body, he would be buried in a forest so that the other living organisms there can use his energy just as he has used energy from them all his life.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T00:34:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Sympathy\u0022 src=\u0022http://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/sympathy.png\u0022 title=\u0022Excellent recovery: ... which we could try to use to somehow save your original brother!\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gaarst","CreatedById":126740,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T00:49:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA physicist would start talking about entropy and ruin everyone\u0027s day (someone\u0027s dead, so how further can it be ruined anyway?).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T01:06:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222649718\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467032541\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002259088\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Camacha\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Camacha said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou mean you want a physisicst to remind everyone how futile your life was and that you were nothing more than a temporary collection of energy and information? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for helping with my afterlife-style plans.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, in addition to the hearse with an ice cream truck sound system (to be driven through residential areas), there will also be a lecture on the heat death of the universe.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dispatcher","CreatedById":78707,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T01:56:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe thought, therefore he was. \u00A0Wait, that\u0027s philosophy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T02:27:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222650871\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467078987\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278707\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dispatcher\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n30 minutes ago, Dispatcher said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe thought, therefore he was. \u00A0Wait, that\u0027s philosophy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*weeping parents suddenly stop and stare at you*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Camacha","CreatedById":59088,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T10:00:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222650412\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467061234\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI once heard Neil DeGrasse Tyson say if he had to be sentenced to death, but could choose what happened to his body, he would be buried in a forest so that the other living organisms there can use his energy just as he has used energy from them all his life.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am not sure why you need to be sentenced for death to do that, but I came to the same conclusion years ago. Your body will return to dust whatever the method of your choosing is, so why not optimize the usefulness of the resources of your body when you no longer need or use them?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T19:11:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222651248\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467108012\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002259088\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Camacha\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Camacha said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0...why not optimize the usefulness of the resources of your body when you no longer need or use them?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause I\u0027d rather be embalmed, mummified, and placed in Red Square for generations of Russians to stare at.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat, you mean you wouldn\u0027t want to do that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-28T21:40:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222651933\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467141089\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause I\u0027d rather be embalmed, mummified, and placed in Red Square for generations of Russians to stare at.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat, you mean you wouldn\u0027t want to do that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAw damn, I forgot about that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T09:43:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222651933\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467141089\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause I\u0027d rather be embalmed, mummified, and placed in Red Square for generations of Russians to stare at.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat, you mean you wouldn\u0027t want to do that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne word: Pyramids.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Camacha","CreatedById":59088,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T10:57:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222651933\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467141089\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-user